  "Description": {
    "English": "Ancient words are carved into this <span class=\"name name-stellar\">living document</span>. They read:<br><br>'The dust was choking. <br>Our eyes reddened and watered. <br>But the truth was inescapable.<br>The veins of the Atlas had surfaced.'",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "这份<span class=\"name name-stellar\">活经文</span>上刻着古老的文字。上面写道：<br><br>“沙尘蔽日。<br>吾等之眼不禁红肿泪流。<br>但真相岂能轻易逃避。<br>阿特拉斯的血脉再次现身。”",
    "TraditionalChinese": "被刻進<span class=\"name name-stellar\">活體文件</span>的古老文字。上頭刻著：<br><br>「塵土飛揚，飛沙走石。<br>我們的雙眼紅腫濕潤。<br>但眼前的事實無可置疑。<br>寰宇血脈已浮出地面。」"
  },
